{
  "chapter": 2,
  "chapter_summary": "第二章以唐缺与老祖宗的对话展开。唐缺向老祖宗汇报两件事：李玉堂住进花园后心事重重，且出手救了上官刃。唐缺据此推断李玉堂不是赵无忌，但老祖宗认为推理过于单一，提出李玉堂可能不想上官刃死在别人手上或死得太痛快。老祖宗进一步质疑袁三调查结果的可靠性，担心收买的内线可能已被大风堂反收买，又指出上官刃知道袁三的行踪。唐缺追问上官刃投靠唐家是否有假，老祖宗坦言最怕上官刃与李玉堂联合卧底。此时袁三失踪的消息更使老祖宗起了疑心。最终老祖宗决定按兵不动，静候唐傲归来裁决，因为唐傲的判断从来没有出过错。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_que",
      "speaker_name": "唐缺",
      "listener": "char_lao_zu_zong",
      "text": "报告老祖宗，发现了两件事。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 2,
      "line_end": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_zu_zong",
      "speaker_name": "老祖宗",
      "listener": "char_tang_que",
      "text": "哪两件？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 4,
      "line_end": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_que",
      "speaker_name": "唐缺",
      "listener": "char_lao_zu_zong",
      "text": "第一，住进花园以后，李玉堂忽然变得心事重重的样子。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 6,
      "line_end": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_zu_zong",
      "speaker_name": "老祖宗",
      "listener": "char_tang_que",
      "text": "还有呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 8,
      "line_end": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_que",
      "speaker_name": "唐缺",
      "listener": "char_lao_zu_zong",
      "text": "他果然出手去救上官刃。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_zu_zong",
      "speaker_name": "老祖宗",
      "listener": "char_tang_que",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 12
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_que",
      "speaker_name": "唐缺",
      "listener": "char_lao_zu_zong",
      "text": "现在他的身份应该不会有疑问了吧？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 14,
      "line_end": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_zu_zong",
      "speaker_name": "老祖宗",
      "listener": "char_tang_que",
      "text": "你那么肯定？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_que",
      "speaker_name": "唐缺",
      "listener": "char_lao_zu_zong",
      "text": "是呀，他既然不想让上官刃死，这表示他不会是赵无忌。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_zu_zong",
      "speaker_name": "老祖宗",
      "listener": "char_tang_que",
      "text": "不想上官刃死，就推论出他不是赵无忌？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_que",
      "speaker_name": "唐缺",
      "listener": "char_lao_zu_zong",
      "text": "难道还有别的推理？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_zu_zong",
      "speaker_name": "老祖宗",
      "listener": "char_tang_que",
      "text": "当然有。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_que",
      "speaker_name": "唐缺",
      "listener": "char_lao_zu_zong",
      "text": "我不懂。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_zu_zong",
      "speaker_name": "老祖宗",
      "listener": "char_tang_que",
      "text": "也许他不希望上官刃死在别人的手上。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_que",
      "speaker_name": "唐缺",
      "listener": "char_lao_zu_zong",
      "text": "还有吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_zu_zong",
      "speaker_name": "老祖宗",
      "listener": "char_tang_que",
      "text": "也许他不想上官刃死得这么痛快。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_que",
      "speaker_name": "唐缺",
      "listener": "char_lao_zu_zong",
      "text": "老祖宗高见。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_zu_zong",
      "speaker_name": "老祖宗",
      "listener": "char_tang_que",
      "text": "别拍我马屁，我看你是不太相信我。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_que",
      "speaker_name": "唐缺",
      "listener": "char_lao_zu_zong",
      "text": "我..老祖宗，我们不是已经派人去绩溪查过，证实李玉堂确实是他吗？",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_zu_zong",
      "speaker_name": "老祖宗",
      "listener": "char_tang_que",
      "text": "这是谁说的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_que",
      "speaker_name": "唐缺",
      "listener": "char_lao_zu_zong",
      "text": "我们派去的袁三证实的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_zu_zong",
      "speaker_name": "老祖宗",
      "listener": "char_tang_que",
      "text": "你知道大风堂里有多少我们收买过来的人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_que",
      "speaker_name": "唐缺",
      "listener": "char_lao_zu_zong",
      "text": "四十七个。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_zu_zong",
      "speaker_name": "老祖宗",
      "listener": "char_tang_que",
      "text": "我们能收买大风堂的人，大风堂的人难道不会收买我们的人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_que",
      "speaker_name": "唐缺",
      "listener": "char_lao_zu_zong",
      "text": "你是说袁三被他们收买？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_zu_zong",
      "speaker_name": "老祖宗",
      "listener": "char_tang_que",
      "text": "我没有说。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_que",
      "speaker_name": "唐缺",
      "listener": "char_lao_zu_zong",
      "text": "那..",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_zu_zong",
      "speaker_name": "老祖宗",
      "listener": "char_tang_que",
      "text": "我只是说未尝没有这个可能。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_que",
      "speaker_name": "唐缺",
      "listener": "char_lao_zu_zong",
      "text": "可是派袁三去没有外人知道呀。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_zu_zong",
      "speaker_name": "老祖宗",
      "listener": "char_tang_que",
      "text": "有。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_que",
      "speaker_name": "唐缺",
      "listener": "char_lao_zu_zong",
      "text": "谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_zu_zong",
      "speaker_name": "老祖宗",
      "listener": "char_tang_que",
      "text": "上官刃。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_que",
      "speaker_name": "唐缺",
      "listener": "char_lao_zu_zong",
      "text": "他？他怎么会呢？他怎么会替赵无忌隐瞒身份？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_zu_zong",
      "speaker_name": "老祖宗",
      "listener": "char_tang_que",
      "text": "我们的想法都单一了，万一他不是赵无忌呢？",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_que",
      "speaker_name": "唐缺",
      "listener": "char_lao_zu_zong",
      "text": "老祖宗，您把我弄糊涂了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_zu_zong",
      "speaker_name": "老祖宗",
      "listener": "char_tang_que",
      "text": "照我们接获的情报，赵无忌确实要杀上官刃报父仇，对不对？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_que",
      "speaker_name": "唐缺",
      "listener": "char_lao_zu_zong",
      "text": "是呀。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_zu_zong",
      "speaker_name": "老祖宗",
      "listener": "char_tang_que",
      "text": "上官刃来投靠我们，为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_que",
      "speaker_name": "唐缺",
      "listener": "char_lao_zu_zong",
      "text": "因为他认为大风堂撑不下去，早晚会被我们击溃，所以杀了赵简表示诚心投靠我们。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_zu_zong",
      "speaker_name": "老祖宗",
      "listener": "char_tang_que",
      "text": "但愿真的如此。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_que",
      "speaker_name": "唐缺",
      "listener": "char_lao_zu_zong",
      "text": "难道还有假不成？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_zu_zong",
      "speaker_name": "老祖宗",
      "listener": "char_tang_que",
      "text": "任何事都小心一点比较妥当。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_que",
      "speaker_name": "唐缺",
      "listener": "char_lao_zu_zong",
      "text": "那你刚刚说的..",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_zu_zong",
      "speaker_name": "老祖宗",
      "listener": "char_tang_que",
      "text": "我就怕上官刃别有企图，那李玉堂是来和他联合卧底的。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_que",
      "speaker_name": "唐缺",
      "listener": "char_lao_zu_zong",
      "text": "这怎么可能？李玉堂是我们派他去做上官刃的总管的。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_zu_zong",
      "speaker_name": "老祖宗",
      "listener": "char_tang_que",
      "text": "这就是我说的，我们的想法太钻到一个地方去了，我们只猜想他是赵无忌，故意派他去伺候上官刃来试探他，而如果他不是赵无忌，而刚好是要来卧底的，那我们岂不错了？",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_que",
      "speaker_name": "唐缺",
      "listener": "char_lao_zu_zong",
      "text": "我不相信上官刃是来卧底的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_zu_zong",
      "speaker_name": "老祖宗",
      "listener": "char_tang_que",
      "text": "我也不相信，但最近发生了一件事，却使我起了怀疑之心。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_que",
      "speaker_name": "唐缺",
      "listener": "char_lao_zu_zong",
      "text": "什么事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_zu_zong",
      "speaker_name": "老祖宗",
      "listener": "char_tang_que",
      "text": "袁三失踪了，他的信是利用鸽子传了回来，但他的人却一直没有回来。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_que",
      "speaker_name": "唐缺",
      "listener": "char_lao_zu_zong",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_zu_zong",
      "speaker_name": "老祖宗",
      "listener": "char_tang_que",
      "text": "所以我对上官刃和李玉堂又开始怀疑了。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_que",
      "speaker_name": "唐缺",
      "listener": "char_lao_zu_zong",
      "text": "对，假如袁三被杀了，最大的嫌疑人是上官刃。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_zu_zong",
      "speaker_name": "老祖宗",
      "listener": "char_tang_que",
      "text": "不错，不过，袁三是个好赌之人，也许在路上赌昏了头也说不定。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_que",
      "speaker_name": "唐缺",
      "listener": "char_lao_zu_zong",
      "text": "那..",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_zu_zong",
      "speaker_name": "老祖宗",
      "listener": "char_tang_que",
      "text": "所以我决定再等一天，明天，一定有他的消息，不管是他本人回来，或者是他被杀的消息传回来。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_que",
      "speaker_name": "唐缺",
      "listener": "char_lao_zu_zong",
      "text": "老祖宗已经派人去调查了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_zu_zong",
      "speaker_name": "老祖宗",
      "listener": "char_tang_que",
      "text": "昨天就派了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_que",
      "speaker_name": "唐缺",
      "listener": "char_lao_zu_zong",
      "text": "那我们该怎么对付李玉堂？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_zu_zong",
      "speaker_name": "老祖宗",
      "listener": "char_tang_que",
      "text": "什么也不做，等。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_que",
      "speaker_name": "唐缺",
      "listener": "char_lao_zu_zong",
      "text": "等？等什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_zu_zong",
      "speaker_name": "老祖宗",
      "listener": "char_tang_que",
      "text": "等一个人。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_que",
      "speaker_name": "唐缺",
      "listener": "char_lao_zu_zong",
      "text": "一个人？谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_zu_zong",
      "speaker_name": "老祖宗",
      "listener": "char_tang_que",
      "text": "唐傲。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 146
    },
